Author: Coinet
Title: [ANN] [COT] COINET | Coinet Financing platform
Body: COINET FINANCING PLATFORM  www.coinet.network  We are entering a new era of financing ideas / projects that intend to carry out DAICO and do not have the necessary funds, through the construction of a p2p decentralized platform where entrepreneurs and investors are connected.  CFP (Coinet Financing Platform) is a decentralized financing platform, P2P that will directly connect investors and project owners. The platform will create an environment of trust by facilitating transparency between the parties and rewarding performance.  SOLUTION  For the Investor. So far you know and invest in the project from the DAICO. COINET FINANCING PLATFORM allows you to know and invest in the project before the Whitepaper.  For the idea / project owner. You just have to make an effort to have a great idea / project. The funds you need to make it known are acquired in COINET FINANCING PLATFORM.  ADVANTAGES OF COINET FINANCING PLATFORM  Evaluation and assessment of potential projects without cost. A multidisciplinary team evaluates your project in case of not fulfilling the requirements the Coinet team will not abandon you, we will give you the result of the evaluation so that you cover the deficiencies found.  High speed at low cost.  Being based on the Stellar platform, we guarantee fast transactions with very competitive commissions in the crypto market.  P2P platform . CFP allows project owners and investors to conduct transactions without intermediaries.  Bifrost of Stellar.  It allows to create a scrow contrac or deposit in guarantee of the funds obtained in the currency of origin and until the conditions are not fulfilled in the intelligent contract these funds will not be changed to COT Coin and delivered to the suppliers.  Proof and Source system.  CFP allows through this system that the investor community are the only ones who have the decision to approve based on a vote by proof check of progress and fulfillment of goals.  Protection and security.  The Blockchain technology ensures the total registration of transactions without manipulation of third parties and protects the movements of users within the CFP.  TOKEN  Name: COT Supply: 10.000.000 no more tokens will be issued Price: 0,5 USD Network: Stellar Consensus Protocol: SCP  SOCIAL NETWORKS  TWITTER: https://twitter.com/grupocoinet FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/coinet.network/ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/grupocoinet/ TELEGRAM: https://t.me/GrupoCoinet  AIRDROP COMING SOON  COINET is releasing 200 COT tokens to members of the community.  Create an account at coinet.network, follow the instructions to get 25 COT, complete some simple tasks on social networks to get up to 125 COT tokens. Obtain 20 COT tokens for each reference.   Step by step guide: Visit the coinet.network website. Send your data and registration. You will get 25 COT tokens. Join your Telegram group to receive 25 COT tokens. Follow them on Twitter and like them on your Facebook page to get 100 COT tokens. Get 20 COT tokens for each friend referred. At the end of the public sale (June 29, 2018) you will receive an email with a link to create a Wallet with the COT coin earned.
